metadata.name: Aera starlight
metadata.description:
In the vast dark universe, There’s a star that likes the spirit of all planets.
Her name is Aera. She’s like a star among millions of universes.
Aera's light helped dispel the darkness and fear of those people.
Even in the darkest part, Aera will never abandon them.
No matter where they are, Aera's light will always reach everyone.


Aerazuki contest  by Aeralytx
